A vast, luminous digital cityscape viewed from above at dusk, rendered in warm Studio Ghibli watercolor style with soft edges and gentle gradients. Interconnected floating platforms and pathways form an intricate web resembling a neural network, each node glowing with amber and teal lights. Tiny silhouetted figures walk along the bridges between structures, suggesting a thriving internal community. Organic vines and small gardens grow on the platforms, blending technology with nature. In the foreground, a solitary figure stands on an observation deck, gazing out at this harmonious digital ecosystem. Wispy clouds drift between the structures, and paper lanterns float upward, casting gentle reflections. The overall mood is one of wonder, connection, and quiet pride in something carefully built and beautifully functional.
